<lb n="0722a11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note n="0722003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋四【明】</note><note n="0722003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四【大】，佛說四【明】</note><app n="0722003"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛說四</rdg></app>十二章<note n="0722004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（序）【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0722004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經序【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0722004"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">經序</rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0722a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0722a13" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0722005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔後漢…譯〕十四字【宋】【元】【宮】，〔後漢西域沙門〕－【明】</note><note n="0722005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後漢西域沙門迦葉摩騰共法蘭譯【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】，迦葉摩騰共法蘭譯【明】</note><app n="0722005"><lem wit="【大】">後漢西域沙門迦葉摩騰共<note n="0722006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（竺）＋法蘭【明】</note><note n="0722006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法蘭【大】，竺法蘭【明】</note><app n="0722006"><lem wit="【大】">法蘭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">竺法蘭</rdg></app><note n="0722007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（奉詔）＋譯【明】</note><note n="0722007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譯【大】，奉詔譯【明】</note><app n="0722007"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">奉詔譯</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">迦葉摩騰共法蘭譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0722a14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><note n="0722008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔昔漢…也〕百六十一字－【明】</note><note n="0722008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（昔漢…也）百六十一字【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0722008" cb:word-count="161"><lem wit="【大】"><p xml:id="pT17p0722a1401">昔漢孝明皇帝夜夢見神人，身體有金色，
<lb n="0722a15" ed="T"/>項有日光，飛在殿前，意中欣然，甚悅之。明日
<lb n="0722a16" ed="T"/>問群臣：「此為何神也？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0722a1609" rend="inline">有通人傅毅曰：「臣聞天
<lb n="0722a17" ed="T"/>竺有得道者，號曰佛，輕舉能飛，殆將其神
<lb n="0722a18" ed="T"/>也。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0722a1802" rend="inline">於是上悟，即遣使者<note n="0722009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">張騫＝蔡愔【元】</note><note n="0722009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">張騫【大】，蔡愔【元】</note><app n="0722009"><lem wit="【大】">張騫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">蔡愔</rdg></app>、羽林中郎將
<lb n="0722a19" ed="T"/>秦景博士弟子王遵等十二人，至大月支國
<lb n="0722a20" ed="T"/>寫取佛經四十二章。在第十四石函中登起
<lb n="0722a21" ed="T"/>立塔寺，於是道法流布，處處修立佛寺。遠
<lb n="0722a22" ed="T"/>人伏化願為臣妾者，不可稱數，國內清寧，含
<lb n="0722a23" ed="T"/>識之類蒙恩受賴于今不絕也。</p></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0722a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722a2401"><note n="0722010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（四十二章經後漢沙門迦葉摩騰共竺法蘭譯）＋佛【宋】【元】【宮】，（爾時世尊，既成道已，作是思惟，離欲寂靜，是最為勝，住大禪定，降諸魔道今轉法輪度眾生於鹿野苑中，為憍陳如等五人，轉四諦法輪，而證道果，時復有比丘所說諸疑，陳佛進止，世尊教詔，一一開悟，合掌敬諾而順尊勅，爾時世尊，為說真經四十二章）九十七字＋佛【明】</note><note n="0722010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，四十二章經後漢沙門迦葉摩騰共竺法蘭譯佛【宋】【元】【宮】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->（爾時世尊，既成道已，作是思惟，離欲寂靜，是最為勝，住大禪定，降諸魔道今轉法輪度眾生於鹿野苑中，為憍陳如等五人，轉四諦法輪，而證道果，時復有比丘所說諸疑，陳佛進止，世尊教詔，一一開悟，合掌敬諾而順尊勅，爾時世尊，為說真經四十二章）九十七字＋佛【明】</note><app n="0722010"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">四十二章經後漢沙門迦葉摩騰共竺法蘭譯佛</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">爾時世尊，既成道已，作是思惟，離欲寂靜，是最為勝，住大禪定，降諸魔道今轉法輪度眾生於鹿野苑中，為憍陳如等五人，轉四諦法輪，而證道果，時復有比丘所說諸疑，陳佛進止，世尊教詔，一一開悟，合掌敬諾而順尊勅，爾時世尊，為說真經四十二章佛</rdg></app>言：「辭親<note n="0722011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">出家＝去家【宮】</note><note n="0722011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">出家【大】，去家【宮】</note><app n="0722011"><lem wit="【大】">出家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">去家</rdg></app>為<note n="0722012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（識心達本解無為法）【明】</note><note n="0722012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道【大】，道識心達本解無為法【明】</note><app n="0722012"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">道識心達本解無為法</rdg></app>，名曰沙門，常行二
<lb n="0722a25" ed="T"/>百五十戒，為四真道行，進志清淨，成<note n="0722013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿羅漢〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0722013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿羅漢【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0722013"><lem wit="【大】">阿羅
<lb n="0722a26" ed="T"/>漢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0722014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛言）＋阿【明】</note><note n="0722014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿【大】，佛言阿【明】</note><app n="0722014"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛言阿</rdg></app>羅漢者，能飛行變化，住壽命，動天地；
<lb n="0722a27" ed="T"/>次為阿那含，阿那含者，壽終魂靈<note n="0722015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝生【宮】</note><note n="0722015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，生【宮】</note><app n="0722015"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">生</rdg></app>十九
<lb n="0722a28" ed="T"/>天，於彼得阿羅漢；次為斯陀含，斯陀含者，一
<lb n="0722a29" ed="T"/>上一還，即得阿羅漢；次為須陀洹，須陀洹者，
<pb n="0722b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0784.0722b"/>
<lb n="0722b01" ed="T"/>七死七生，便得阿羅漢；愛欲斷者，譬如四支
<lb n="0722b02" ed="T"/>斷，不復用之。」</p>
<lb n="0722b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722b0301"><note n="0722016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛言，出家沙門者，斷欲去愛，識自心源，達佛深理，悟佛無為，內無所得，外無所求，心不繫道，亦不結業，無念無作，無修無證不，歷諸位而自崇最，名之為道）五十九字＋佛【明】</note><note n="0722016" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->（佛言，出家沙門者，斷欲去愛，識自心源，達佛深理，悟佛無為，內無所得，外無所求，心不繫道，亦不結業，無念無作，無修無證不，歷諸位而自崇最，名之為道）五十九字＋佛【明】</note><app n="0722016"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛言，出家沙門者，斷欲去愛，識自心源，達佛深理，悟佛無為，內無所得，外無所求，心不繫道，亦不結業，無念無作，無修無證不，歷諸位而自崇最，名之為道佛</rdg></app>言：「<note n="0722017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（剃）＋除【明】</note><note n="0722017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】，剃除【明】</note><app n="0722017"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">剃除</rdg></app>鬚<note n="0722018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髮＋（而）【明】</note><note n="0722018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髮【大】，髮而【明】</note><app n="0722018"><lem wit="【大】">髮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">髮而</rdg></app>，為沙門，受<note n="0722019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道法＝佛法者【明】</note><note n="0722019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道法【大】，佛法者【明】</note><app n="0722019"><lem wit="【大】">道法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛法者</rdg></app>，去世資
<lb n="0722b04" ed="T"/>財，乞求取足，日中一食，樹下一宿，慎不再
<lb n="0722b05" ed="T"/>矣！使人愚弊者，愛與欲也。」</p>
<lb n="0722b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722b0601">佛言：「眾生以十事為善，亦以十事為惡。<note n="0722020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（何者為十）＋身【明】</note><note n="0722020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身【大】，何者為十身【明】</note><app n="0722020"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">何者為十身</rdg></app>
<lb n="0722b07" ed="T"/>三、口四、意三。身三者：殺、盜、婬；口四者：兩
<lb n="0722b08" ed="T"/>舌、惡罵、妄言、綺語；意三者：嫉、恚、癡，不信三
<lb n="0722b09" ed="T"/>尊，以邪為真。優婆塞行五事，不懈退，至十事，
<lb n="0722b10" ed="T"/>必得道也。」</p>
<lb n="0722b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722b1101">佛言：「人有眾過，而不自悔，頓止其心，罪來歸
<lb n="0722b12" ed="T"/>身，猶水歸海，自成深廣<note n="0722021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣＝何能免離【明】</note><note n="0722021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矣【大】，何能免離【明】</note><app n="0722021"><lem wit="【大】">矣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">何能免離</rdg></app>；有惡知非，改過
<lb n="0722b13" ed="T"/>得善，罪日消滅，後會得道也。」</p>
<lb n="0722b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722b1401">佛言：「人<note n="0722022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愚＝遇【宮】</note><note n="0722022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愚【大】，遇【宮】</note><app n="0722022"><lem wit="【大】">愚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">遇</rdg></app><note n="0722023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾以＝以吾【明】</note><note n="0722023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾以【大】，以吾【明】</note><app n="0722023"><lem wit="【大】">吾以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">以吾</rdg></app>為不善，<note n="0722024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾＝善【宮】</note><note n="0722024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾【大】，善【宮】</note><app n="0722024"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">善</rdg></app>以四等慈護
<lb n="0722b15" ed="T"/>濟之；重以惡來者，吾重以善往，福德之氣，常
<lb n="0722b16" ed="T"/>在此也；害氣重殃，反在于彼。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0722b1612" rend="inline">有<note n="0722025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（愚）＋人【明】</note><note n="0722025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，愚人【明】</note><app n="0722025"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">愚人</rdg></app>聞佛道
<lb n="0722b17" ed="T"/>守大仁慈，以惡來，以善往，故來罵。<note n="0722026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（佛）【明】</note><note n="0722026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，佛佛【明】</note><app n="0722026"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛佛</rdg></app>默然
<lb n="0722b18" ed="T"/>不答，愍之癡冥狂愚使然。罵止，問曰：「子以禮
<lb n="0722b19" ed="T"/>從人，其人不納，<note n="0722027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">實＝寶【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0722027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">實【大】，寶【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0722027"><lem wit="【大】">實</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">寶</rdg></app><note n="0722028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮＝理【明】</note><note n="0722028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮【大】，理【明】</note><app n="0722028"><lem wit="【大】">禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">理</rdg></app>如之乎？」曰：「持歸。」「今
<lb n="0722b20" ed="T"/>子罵我，我亦不納，子自持歸，禍子身矣！猶響
<lb n="0722b21" ed="T"/>應聲，影之追形，終無免離，慎為惡也。」</p>
<lb n="0722b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722b2201">佛言：「惡人害賢者，猶仰天而唾，唾不污天，
<lb n="0722b23" ed="T"/>還污己身；逆風坋人，塵不污彼，還坋于身。賢
<lb n="0722b24" ed="T"/>者不<note n="0722029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔可〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0722029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">可【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0722029"><lem wit="【大】">可</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>毀，<note n="0722b2401" resp="CBETA" type="add">禍【CB】【麗-CB】，過【大】</note><app n="0722b2401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">禍<note type="cf1">K19n0778_p0865c04</note><note type="cf2">T39n1794_p0518c17</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">過</rdg></app>必滅己也。」</p>
<lb n="0722b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722b2501">佛言：「夫人為道務博愛，博哀施德莫大施。守
<lb n="0722b26" ed="T"/>志奉道，其福甚大；覩人施道，助之歡喜，亦得
<lb n="0722b27" ed="T"/>福報。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0722b2703" rend="inline">質曰：「彼福不當<note n="0722030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">減＝滅【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0722030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">減【大】，滅【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0722030"><lem wit="【大】">減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">滅</rdg></app>乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0722b2711" rend="inline">佛言：「猶<note n="0722031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝如【明】</note><note n="0722031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，如【明】</note><app n="0722031"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">如</rdg></app>炬
<lb n="0722b28" ed="T"/>火，數千百人，各以炬來，取其火去，熟食、除冥；
<lb n="0722b29" ed="T"/>彼火如故，福亦如之。」</p>
<pb n="0722c" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0784.0722c"/>
<lb n="0722c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722c0101">佛言：「飯凡人百不如飯一善人，飯善人千不
<lb n="0722c02" ed="T"/>如飯持五戒者一人，飯持五戒者萬人不如
<lb n="0722c03" ed="T"/>飯一須陀洹，飯須陀洹百萬不如飯一斯陀
<lb n="0722c04" ed="T"/>含，飯斯陀含千萬不如飯一阿那含，飯阿那
<lb n="0722c05" ed="T"/>含一億不如飯一阿羅漢，飯阿羅漢十億不
<lb n="0722c06" ed="T"/>如飯辟支佛一人，飯辟支佛百億<note n="0722032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不如…千億〕十六字－【明】</note><note n="0722032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（不如…千億）十六字【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0722032" cb:word-count="16"><lem wit="【大】">不如以
<lb n="0722c07" ed="T"/>三尊之教度其一世二親，<note n="0722033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">教＋（親）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0722033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教親【CB】【麗-CB】【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，教【大】</note><app n="0722033"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">教親<note type="cf1">K19n0778_p0865c18</note><note type="cf2">T53n2122_p0655b21</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">教</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">教親</rdg></app>千億</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不如飯一
<lb n="0722c08" ed="T"/>佛——學願求佛，欲濟眾生也。飯善人福最深重，
<lb n="0722c09" ed="T"/>凡人事天地鬼神，不如孝其<note n="0722034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親矣＝二親【明】</note><note n="0722034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">親矣【大】，二親【明】</note><app n="0722034"><lem wit="【大】">親矣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二親</rdg></app>，二親最神
<lb n="0722c10" ed="T"/>也。」</p>
<lb n="0722c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722c1101">佛言：「天下有五難：貧窮布施難、豪貴學道
<lb n="0722c12" ed="T"/>難、<note n="0722035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">制＝利【宋】【元】，判【明】【宮】</note><note n="0722035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">制【大】，利【宋】【元】，判【明】【宮】</note><app n="0722035"><lem wit="【大】">制</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">利</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">判</rdg></app>命不死難、得覩佛經難、生值佛世<note n="0722036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">難＋（忍色離欲難，見好不求難，有勢不臨難，被辱不瞋難，觸事無心難，廣學博究難，不輕未學難，除滅我慢難，會善知識難，見性學道難，對境不動難，隨化度人難，心行平等難，不說是非難）七十字【明】</note><note n="0722036" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->難＋（忍色離欲難，見好不求難，有勢不臨難，被辱不瞋難，觸事無心難，廣學博究難，不輕未學難，除滅我慢難，會善知識難，見性學道難，對境不動難，隨化度人難，心行平等難，不說是非難）七十字【明】</note><app n="0722036"><lem wit="【大】">難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">難忍色離欲難，見好不求難，有勢不臨難，被辱不瞋難，觸事無心難，廣學博究難，不輕未學難，除滅我慢難，會善知識難，見性學道難，對境不動難，隨化度人難，心行平等難，不說是非難</rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb n="0722c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722c1301">有沙門問佛：「以何緣得道？奈何知宿命？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0722c1316" rend="inline">佛
<lb n="0722c14" ed="T"/>言：「道無<note n="0722037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＋（相）【明】</note><note n="0722037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">形【大】，形相【明】</note><app n="0722037"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">形相</rdg></app>，知之無益，要當守志行；譬如磨
<lb n="0722c15" ed="T"/>鏡，垢去明<note n="0722038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">存＝在【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0722038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">存【大】，在【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0722038"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">在</rdg></app>，即自見形，斷欲守空，即見道
<lb n="0722c16" ed="T"/>真，知宿命矣。」</p>
<lb n="0722c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0722c1701">佛言：「何者為善？<note n="0722039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】</note><note n="0722039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】，惟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0722039"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>行道善。何者最大？志與
<lb n="0722c18" ed="T"/>道合大。何者多力？忍辱最健，忍者無<note n="0722040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＝惡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0722040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨【大】，惡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0722040"><lem wit="【大】">怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡</rdg></app>，必
<lb n="0722c19" ed="T"/>為<note n="0722041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝最【宋】</note><note n="0722041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，最【宋】</note><app n="0722041"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">最</rdg></app>尊。何者最明？心垢除、惡行滅，內清淨
<lb n="0722c20" ed="T"/>無瑕；未有天地，逮于今日，十方所有，未<note n="0722042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見之萌＝甞不見【明】</note><note n="0722042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見之萌【大】，甞不見【明】</note><app n="0722042"><lem wit="【大】">見
<pb n="0723a" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0784.0723a"/>
<lb n="0723a01" ed="T"/>之萌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">甞不見</rdg></app>，得無不知、無不見、無不聞，得一切智，可
<lb n="0723a02" ed="T"/>謂明乎。」</p>
<lb n="0723a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a0301">佛言：「人懷愛欲不見<note n="0723001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（者）【明】</note><note n="0723001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道【大】，道者【明】</note><app n="0723001"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">道者</rdg></app>，譬如濁水，以五彩投
<lb n="0723a04" ed="T"/>其中，致力<note n="0723002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">攪＝捁【宋】，梏【宮】</note><note n="0723002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攪【大】，捁【宋】，梏【宮】</note><app n="0723002"><lem wit="【大】">攪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">捁</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">梏</rdg></app>之，眾人共臨水上，無能覩其影
<lb n="0723a05" ed="T"/><note n="0723003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【明】</note><note n="0723003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0723003"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>；愛欲交錯，心中為濁，故不見<note n="0723004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（若人漸解懺悔來近知識）【明】</note><note n="0723004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道【大】，道若人漸解懺悔來近知識【明】</note><app n="0723004"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">道若人漸解懺悔來近知識</rdg></app>；水澄穢
<lb n="0723a06" ed="T"/>除，清淨無垢，即自見形。猛火著釜下，中水<note n="0723005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">踊＝涌【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0723005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">踊【大】，涌【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0723005"><lem wit="【大】">踊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">涌</rdg></app>
<lb n="0723a07" ed="T"/>躍，以布覆上，眾生照臨，亦無覩其影者；心中
<lb n="0723a08" ed="T"/>本有三毒<note n="0723006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">涌＝踊【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0723006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">涌【大】，踊【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0723006"><lem wit="【大】">涌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">踊</rdg></app>沸在內，五蓋覆外，終不見道；
<lb n="0723a09" ed="T"/><note n="0723007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要＝惡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0723007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">要【大】，惡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0723007"><lem wit="【大】">要</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡</rdg></app>心垢盡，乃知魂靈所從來，生死所趣向，諸
<lb n="0723a10" ed="T"/>佛國土、道德所在耳。」</p>
<lb n="0723a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a1101">佛言：「夫為道者，譬如持炬火入冥室中，其冥
<lb n="0723a12" ed="T"/>即滅而明猶<note n="0723008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝存【三】【宮】</note><note n="0723008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0723008"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">存</rdg></app>，學道見諦，愚癡都滅，<note n="0723009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得無不見＝無不明矣【明】</note><note n="0723009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得無不見【大】，無不明矣【明】</note><app n="0723009"><lem wit="【大】">得無
<lb n="0723a13" ed="T"/>不見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">無不明矣</rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb n="0723a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a1401">佛言：「吾何念念道？吾何行行道？吾何言言道？
<lb n="0723a15" ed="T"/>吾念諦道，不<note n="0723010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忽＝忘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0723010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忽【大】，忘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0723010"><lem wit="【大】">忽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忘</rdg></app>須臾也。」</p>
<lb n="0723a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a1601">佛言：「覩天地念非常，覩山川念非常，覩<note n="0723011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">万＝方【宋】</note><note n="0723011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">万【大】，方【宋】</note><app n="0723011"><lem wit="【大】">万</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">方</rdg></app>
<lb n="0723a17" ed="T"/>物形體豐熾念非常；執心如此，得道疾矣。」</p>
<lb n="0723a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a1801">佛言：「一日行，常念道、行道，遂得信根，其福無
<lb n="0723a19" ed="T"/>量。」</p>
<lb n="0723a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a2001">佛言：「熟自念身中四大，名自有名都為無，吾
<lb n="0723a21" ed="T"/>我者寄生，<note n="0723012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0723012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0723012"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>亦不久，其事如幻耳。」</p>
<lb n="0723a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a2201">佛言：「人隨情欲求華名，譬如燒香，眾人聞其
<lb n="0723a23" ed="T"/>香，然香以熏自燒；愚者貪流俗之名譽，不守
<lb n="0723a24" ed="T"/>道真，華名危己之禍，其悔在後時。」</p>
<lb n="0723a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a2501">佛言：「財色之於人，譬如小兒貪刀刃之蜜，甜
<lb n="0723a26" ed="T"/>不足一食之美，然有截舌之患也。」</p>
<lb n="0723a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723a2701">佛言：「人繫於妻子、寶宅之患，甚於牢獄、桎梏、
<lb n="0723a28" ed="T"/><note n="0723013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鋃鐺＝郎當【宋】【宮】，桹檔【明】</note><note n="0723013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鋃鐺【大】，郎當【宋】【宮】，桹檔【明】</note><app n="0723013"><lem wit="【大】">鋃鐺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">郎當</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">桹檔</rdg></app>。牢獄有原赦，妻子情欲雖有虎口之
<lb n="0723a29" ed="T"/>禍，己猶甘心投焉，其罪無赦。」</p>
<pb n="0723b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0784.0723b"/>
<lb n="0723b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b0101">佛言：「愛欲莫甚於色，色之為欲，<note n="0723014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝甚【宮】</note><note n="0723014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，甚【宮】</note><app n="0723014"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">甚</rdg></app>大無外。
<lb n="0723b02" ed="T"/>賴有一矣，假其<note n="0723015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＋（同）【明】</note><note n="0723015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，二同【明】</note><app n="0723015"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二同</rdg></app>，普天之民，無能為道者。」</p>
<lb n="0723b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b0301">佛言：「愛欲之於人，猶執炬火逆風而行。愚者
<lb n="0723b04" ed="T"/>不釋炬，必有燒手之患。貪婬、恚怒、愚癡之毒，
<lb n="0723b05" ed="T"/>處在人身，不早以道除斯禍者，必有危<note n="0723016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殃＝歎【宮】</note><note n="0723016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殃【大】，歎【宮】</note><app n="0723016"><lem wit="【大】">殃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">歎</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0723b06" ed="T"/>猶愚貪執炬，自燒其手<note n="0723017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＋（時有）【明】</note><note n="0723017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也【大】，也時有【明】</note><app n="0723017"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">也時有</rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb n="0723b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b0701">天神獻玉女於佛，欲以試佛意、觀佛道。佛言：
<lb n="0723b08" ed="T"/>「革囊眾穢，爾來何為？以可<note n="0723018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝誑【元】【明】</note><note n="0723018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斯【大】，誑【元】【明】</note><app n="0723018"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">誑</rdg></app>俗，難動六通。
<lb n="0723b09" ed="T"/>去！吾不用爾。」天神<note n="0723019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">踰＝愈【明】</note><note n="0723019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">踰【大】，愈【明】</note><app n="0723019"><lem wit="【大】">踰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">愈</rdg></app>敬佛，因問道意；佛為
<lb n="0723b10" ed="T"/>解釋，即得須陀洹。</p>
<lb n="0723b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b1101">佛言：「夫為道者，猶木在水，尋流而行，不左觸
<lb n="0723b12" ed="T"/>岸，亦不右觸岸；不為人所取，不為鬼神所遮，
<lb n="0723b13" ed="T"/>不為<note n="0723020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洄＝迴【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0723020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洄【大】，迴【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0723020"><lem wit="【大】">洄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">迴</rdg></app>流所住，亦不腐敗，吾保其入海矣。
<lb n="0723b14" ed="T"/>人為道，不為情欲所惑，不為眾邪所誑，精進
<lb n="0723b15" ed="T"/>無疑，吾保其得道矣。」</p>
<lb n="0723b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b1601">佛告沙門：「慎無信汝<note n="0723021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＋（汝）【明】</note><note n="0723021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意【大】，意汝【明】</note><app n="0723021"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">意汝</rdg></app>，意終不可信。慎無
<lb n="0723b17" ed="T"/>與色會，<note n="0723022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔與〕－【明】</note><note n="0723022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0723022"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>色會即禍生。得阿羅漢道，乃可
<lb n="0723b18" ed="T"/>信汝意耳。」</p>
<lb n="0723b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b1901">佛告諸沙門：「慎無視女人，若見無<note n="0723023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視＝見【三】</note><note n="0723023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視【大】，見【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0723023"><lem wit="【大】">視</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">見</rdg></app>。慎無
<lb n="0723b20" ed="T"/>與言，若與言者，勅心正行，曰：『吾為沙門，處于
<lb n="0723b21" ed="T"/>濁世，當如蓮花不為泥所污。老者以為母，長
<lb n="0723b22" ed="T"/>者以為姊，少者<note n="0723024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋為【明】，為＝如【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0723024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為【大】，以為【明】，如【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0723024"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">以為</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">如</rdg></app>妹，幼者<note n="0723025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝如女【宋】【元】【宮】，予【明】</note><note n="0723025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，如女【宋】【元】【宮】，予【明】</note><app n="0723025"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">如女</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">予</rdg></app>，敬之以禮。』意
<lb n="0723b23" ed="T"/>殊當諦惟觀，自頭至足自視內，彼身何有，
<lb n="0723b24" ed="T"/><note n="0723026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0723026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】，惟【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0723026"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>盛惡露諸不淨種，以釋其<note n="0723027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝音【宋】【元】</note><note n="0723027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意【大】，音【宋】【元】</note><app n="0723027"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">音</rdg></app><note n="0723028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔矣〕－【明】</note><note n="0723028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矣【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0723028"><lem wit="【大】">矣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb n="0723b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b2501">佛言：「人為道去情欲，當如草見<note n="0723029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">火＝大【三】【宮】</note><note n="0723029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">火【大】，大【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0723029"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大</rdg></app>，火來已
<lb n="0723b26" ed="T"/><note n="0723030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">却＝劫【明】</note><note n="0723030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">却【大】，劫【明】</note><app n="0723030"><lem wit="【大】">却</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">劫</rdg></app>。道人見愛欲，必當遠之。」</p>
<lb n="0723b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723b2701">佛言：「人有患婬，情不止，踞斧刃上，以自除其
<lb n="0723b28" ed="T"/>陰。佛謂之曰：『<note n="0723031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（使）【明】</note><note n="0723031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，若使【明】</note><app n="0723031"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">若使</rdg></app>斷陰不如斷心，心為功曹，
<lb n="0723b29" ed="T"/>若止功曹，從者都息；邪心不止，斷陰何益？斯
<pb n="0723c" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0784.0723c"/>
<lb n="0723c01" ed="T"/>須即死？』」佛言：「世俗倒見，如斯癡人。」</p>
<lb n="0723c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c0201">有婬童女與彼男誓，至期不來而自悔曰：「欲
<lb n="0723c03" ed="T"/>吾知爾本，意以思想生，吾不思想爾，即爾而
<lb n="0723c04" ed="T"/>不生。」佛行<note n="0723032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＝速【元】</note><note n="0723032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道【大】，速【元】</note><app n="0723032"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">速</rdg></app>聞之，謂沙門曰：「記之！此迦葉
<lb n="0723c05" ed="T"/>佛偈，流在俗間。」</p>
<lb n="0723c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c0601">佛言：「人從愛欲生憂，從憂生畏。無愛即無憂，
<lb n="0723c07" ed="T"/>不憂即無畏。」</p>
<lb n="0723c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c0801">佛言：「人為道，譬如一人與萬人戰，被<note n="0723033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鉀＝甲【明】</note><note n="0723033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉀【大】，甲【明】</note><app n="0723033"><lem wit="【大】">鉀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">甲</rdg></app>、操兵、
<lb n="0723c09" ed="T"/>出門欲戰，意怯<note n="0723034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">膽＝曕【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0723034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">膽【大】，曕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0723034"><lem wit="【大】">膽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">曕</rdg></app>弱乃自退走，或半道還，
<lb n="0723c10" ed="T"/>或格鬪而死，或得大勝還國高遷。夫人能牢
<lb n="0723c11" ed="T"/>持其心，精銳進行，不惑<note n="0723035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝於【明】</note><note n="0723035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">于【大】，於【明】</note><app n="0723035"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">於</rdg></app>流俗狂愚之言者，
<lb n="0723c12" ed="T"/>欲滅惡盡，必得道矣。」</p>
<lb n="0723c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c1301">有沙門夜誦經<note n="0723036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（甚悲…思歸））十字＝（（其聲悲緊欲悔思返））八字【明】</note><note n="0723036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（甚悲…思歸）十字【大】，其聲悲緊欲悔思返【明】</note><app n="0723036" cb:word-count="10"><lem wit="【大】">甚悲，意有悔疑，欲生思歸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">其聲悲緊欲悔思返</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0723c14" ed="T"/>佛呼沙門問之：「汝處于家將<note n="0723c1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">何【CB】【麗-CB】，阿【大】</note><app n="0723c1401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">何<note type="cf1">K19n0778_p0867a24</note><note type="cf2">T39n1794_p0521c20</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">阿</rdg></app>修為？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0723c1415" rend="inline">對曰：
<lb n="0723c15" ed="T"/>「<note n="0723037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恒＝常【明】</note><note n="0723037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恒【大】，常【明】</note><app n="0723037"><lem wit="【大】">恒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">常</rdg></app>彈琴。」佛言：「<note n="0723038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絃＝弦【明】＊</note><note n="0723038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絃【大】＊，弦【明】＊</note><app n="0723038"><lem wit="【大】">絃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">弦</rdg></app>緩何如？」曰：「不鳴矣。」「<app type="star" corresp="#0723038"><lem wit="【大】">絃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">弦</rdg></app>急
<lb n="0723c16" ed="T"/>何如？」曰：「聲絕矣。」「急緩得中何<note n="0723039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＋（曰）【明】</note><note n="0723039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如【大】，如曰【明】</note><app n="0723039"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">如曰</rdg></app>？」「諸音普<note n="0723040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悲＝矣【宋】【元】【宮】，調【明】</note><note n="0723040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲【大】，矣【宋】【元】【宮】，調【明】</note><app n="0723040"><lem wit="【大】">悲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">矣</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">調</rdg></app>。」
<lb n="0723c17" ed="T"/>佛告沙門：「學道猶然，執心調適，道可得矣。」</p>
<lb n="0723c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c1801">佛言：「夫人為道，猶所鍛鐵漸深，<note n="0723041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">棄＝垂【明】</note><note n="0723041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">棄【大】，垂【明】</note><app n="0723041"><lem wit="【大】">棄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">垂</rdg></app>去垢，成器
<lb n="0723c19" ed="T"/>必好。學道以漸深，去心垢，精進就道。<note n="0723042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暴＝異【明】</note><note n="0723042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暴【大】，異【明】</note><app n="0723042"><lem wit="【大】">暴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">異</rdg></app>即
<lb n="0723c20" ed="T"/>身疲，身疲即意惱，意惱即行退，行退即修
<lb n="0723c21" ed="T"/>罪。」</p>
<lb n="0723c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c2201">佛言：「人為道亦苦，不為道亦苦。惟人自生至
<lb n="0723c23" ed="T"/>老，自老至病，自病至死，其苦無量。心惱積
<lb n="0723c24" ed="T"/>罪，生死不息，其苦難說。」</p>
<lb n="0723c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0723c2501">佛言：「夫人離三惡道得為人難；既得為人，去
<lb n="0723c26" ed="T"/>女即男難；既得為男，六情完具難；六情已具，
<lb n="0723c27" ed="T"/>生中國難；既處中國，值奉佛道難；既奉佛道，
<lb n="0723c28" ed="T"/>值有道之君<note n="0723043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">難＋（既值有道之君）【明】</note><note n="0723043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">難【大】，難既值有道之君【明】</note><app n="0723043"><lem wit="【大】">難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">難既值有道之君</rdg></app>，生菩薩家難；既生菩薩家，
<lb n="0723c29" ed="T"/>以心信三尊、值佛世難。」</p>
<pb n="0724a" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0784.0724a"/>
<lb n="0724a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0724a0101">佛問諸沙門：「人命在幾間？」對曰：「在數日間。」
<lb n="0724a02" ed="T"/>佛言：「子未能為道。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0724a0208" rend="inline">復問一沙門：「人命在幾間？」
<lb n="0724a03" ed="T"/>對曰：「在飯食間。」<note n="0724001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛言＝去【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛言【大】，去【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724001"><lem wit="【大】">佛言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">去</rdg></app>：「子未能為道。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0724a0314" rend="inline">復問一
<lb n="0724a04" ed="T"/>沙門：「人命在幾間？」對曰：「呼吸之間。」佛言：「善
<lb n="0724a05" ed="T"/>哉！子可謂為道者矣。」</p>
<lb n="0724a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0724a0601">佛言：「弟子去，離吾數千里，意念吾戒必得道。
<lb n="0724a07" ed="T"/><note n="0724002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在吾左側＝若在吾側【明】</note><note n="0724002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在吾左側【大】，若在吾側【明】</note><app n="0724002"><lem wit="【大】">在吾左側</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">若在吾側</rdg></app>，意在邪，終不得道。其實在行，近而
<lb n="0724a08" ed="T"/>不行，何益萬分耶！」</p>
<lb n="0724a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0724a0901">佛言：「人為道，猶若食蜜，中邊皆甜。吾經亦爾，
<lb n="0724a10" ed="T"/>其義皆快，行者得道矣。」</p>
<lb n="0724a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0724a1101">佛言：「人為道，能拔愛欲之根，譬如摘懸珠，一
<lb n="0724a12" ed="T"/>一摘之，會有盡時。惡盡，得道也。」</p>
<lb n="0724a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0724a1301">佛言：「諸沙門行道，當如牛負，行深泥中，疲極，
<lb n="0724a14" ed="T"/>不敢左右顧，趣欲離泥，以自蘇息。沙門視情
<lb n="0724a15" ed="T"/>欲，甚於彼泥，直心念道可免眾苦。」</p>
<lb n="0724a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0724a1601">佛言：「吾視<note n="0724003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝王【明】</note><note n="0724003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸【大】，王【明】</note><app n="0724003"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">王</rdg></app>侯之位如<note n="0724004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過客＝塵隙【明】</note><note n="0724004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過客【大】，塵隙【明】</note><app n="0724004"><lem wit="【大】">過客</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">塵隙</rdg></app>，視金玉之寶
<lb n="0724a17" ed="T"/>如<note n="0724005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">礫石＝瓦礫【明】</note><note n="0724005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">礫石【大】，瓦礫【明】</note><app n="0724005"><lem wit="【大】">礫石</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">瓦礫</rdg></app>，視<note n="0724006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">㲲＝紈【明】</note><note n="0724006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">㲲【大】，紈【明】</note><app n="0724006"><lem wit="【大】">㲲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">紈</rdg></app>素之<note n="0724007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好＝服【明】</note><note n="0724007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">好【大】，服【明】</note><app n="0724007"><lem wit="【大】">好</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">服</rdg></app>如弊<note n="0724008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帛＋（視大千世界如一訶子，視四耨水如塗足油，視方便如筏寶聚，視無上乘如夢金帛，視求佛道如眼前花，視求禪定如須彌柱，視求涅槃如晝夜寤，視倒正者如六龍舞，視平等者如一真地，視興化者如四時木，諸大比丘，聞佛所說，歡喜奉行）九十二字【明】</note><note n="0724008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->帛＋（視大千世界如一訶子，視四耨水如塗足油，視方便如筏寶聚，視無上乘如夢金帛，視求佛道如眼前花，視求禪定如須彌柱，視求涅槃如晝夜寤，視倒正者如六龍舞，視平等者如一真地，視興化者如四時木，諸大比丘，聞佛所說，歡喜奉行）九十二字【明】</note><app n="0724008"><lem wit="【大】">帛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">帛視大千世界如一訶子，視四耨水如塗足油，視方便如筏寶聚，視無上乘如夢金帛，視求佛道如眼前花，視求禪定如須彌柱，視求涅槃如晝夜寤，視倒正者如六龍舞，視平等者如一真地，視興化者如四時木，諸大比丘，聞佛所說，歡喜奉行</rdg></app>。」</p></cb:div>
